  "meta_description": "Hilary Duff honors the legacy of Robert Carradine, her co-star in the beloved TV series 'Lizzie McGuire' and the 'Revenge of the Nerds' films.",
  "summary_30w": "Hilary Duff mourns the passing of Robert Carradine, her co-star in the iconic 'Lizzie McGuire' series, highlighting his impact on the show and his acting career.",
  "article": "Hilary Duff, the beloved star of the hit Disney Channel series 'Lizzie McGuire', has paid a heartfelt tribute to her co-star Robert Carradine, who passed away at the age of 68. Carradine, known for his roles in the 'Revenge of the Nerds' films and as Lizzie's father in the beloved TV show, left an indelible mark on the entertainment industry.

