  "article": "In a momentous announcement, NASA has revealed the four astronauts who will embark on the first crewed Moon mission in over 50 years. This historic mission, scheduled for launch in the coming years, will mark a significant milestone in the agency's Artemis program, which aims to establish a sustainable human presence on the lunar surface.

